com.salesforce.androidsdk.analytics.model

Class DeviceAppAttributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.salesforce.androidsdk.analytics.model.DeviceAppAttributes

  • public class DeviceAppAttributes
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents common attributes specific to this app and device. These attributes will be appended to the events stored using this library.

    bhariharan
